Package stind

Class Result<T,S extends Exception>

java.lang.Object
stind.Result<T,S>
Type Parameters:
T - The type to be contained if the Result is Ok
S - The type to be contained if the Result is an error, which must extend Exception
public class Result<T,S extends Exception> extends Object
Type which allows for error handling and error propagation, similar to Rust's Result type. It is intended to avoid the usage of try/catch statements, and instead makes use of the ErrorHandler interface and lambda expressions.
